:"SYS_B_05" AND R.RWRC_OWNR=:3 ) OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM T_ALRT A, T_WKFWTSK W WHERE A.ALRT_ID = W.WTSK_RFRDOBJ_ID AND W.WTSK_RFRDOBJ_TYP=:"SYS_B_06" AND W.WTSK_OBJ_STT IN (:"SYS_B_07", :"SYS_B_08") AND A.ALRT_AFFN_CM=T.case_id AND A.ALRT_OBJ_STT != :"SYS_B_09" AND A.ALRT_OWNR=:4 ) OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM T_NTCE N, T_WKFWTSK W WHERE N.NTC_ID = W.WTSK_RFRDOBJ_ID AND W.WTSK_RFRDOBJ_TYP=:"SYS_B_10" AND W.WTSK_OBJ_STT IN (:"SYS_B_11", :"SYS_B_12") AND N.NTC_AFFN_CM=T.case_id AND N.NTC_OBJ_STT IN (:"SYS_B_13", :"SYS_B_14") AND N.NTC_OWNR=:5 ) ) ) recordUpdated, T.NEXT_REVIEW_DATE nextReviewDate, (SELECT count(*) FROM T_REVWREC R WHERE R.RWRC_RFRDOBJ_ID=T.CMBB_ID AND R.RWRC_RFRDOBJ_TYP IN(:"SYS_B_15", :"SYS_B_16", :"SYS_B_17", :"SYS_B_18") AND R.RWRC_OBJ_STT !=:"SYS_B_19") pendingReviews, T.CMBB_SVTY severityId, T.CMBB_OBJ_STT stateId, T.CMBB_PITY priorityId, T.PARTICIPATION participationId, T.STAGE stageId, T.PARTICIPATIONSTATUS participationStatusId, T.TGT_INTERVENTION AS targetInterventionId, T.TIMING AS timingId FROM T_CM_BASEBASE T LEFT OUTER JOIN T_TNFRREC transfer ON transfer.TRRC_ID = coalesce(T.case_tnfr, t.cmpr_tnfr) WHERE (coalesce(T.case_ownr, t.cmpr_ownr, t.csrq_ownr, t.cmpq_o wnr) = :6 AND T.cmbb_obj_stt in (:"SYS_B_20", :"SYS_B_21")) OR (transfer.trrc_rcpt = :7 AND T.cmbb_obj_stt=:"SYS_B_22") OR (T.CMBB_ID IN (SELECT RWRC_RFRDOBJ_ID FROM T_REVWREC WHERE RWRC_OWNR=:8 AND RWRC_RFRDOBJ_TYP in (:"SYS_B_23", :"SYS_B_24", :"SYS_B_25", :"SYS_B_26") AND RWRC_OBJ_STT IN (:"SYS_B_27", :"SYS_B_28")) AND T.cmbb_obj_stt in (:"SYS_B_29", :"SYS_B_30")) OR (T.CMBB_ID IN (SELECT ALRT_AFFN_CM FROM T_ALRT WHERE ALRT_AFFN_CM IS NOT NULL AND ALRT_OBJ_STT != :"SYS_B_31" AND ALRT_OWNR=:9 )) OR (T.CMBB_ID IN (SELECT NTC_AFFN_CM FROM T_NTCE WHERE NTC_OWNR=:10 AND NTC_OBJ_STT IN (:"SYS_B_32", :"SYS_B_33"))) ) BASE WHERE :"SYS_B_34"=:"SYS_B_35" ) order by sortDate fetch first :"SYS_B_36" rows only) MYWORK
